Package pl.edu.pwr.student.UI

Interface UiAvailable

All Known Implementing Classes:
AND, BasicGate, BasicPassThrough, Clock, Delay, LED, NAND, NOR, NOT, OR, Speaker, Switch, VirtualIO, XNOR, XOR
public interface UiAvailable
The UiAvailable interface defines methods for any element that can be placed on a canvas. This interface is implemented by classes representing logic gates, and other components.
